# Workforce Management API Test Scripts
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension or any HTTP client

### Get Welcome Message
GET http://localhost:5000/
Accept: application/json

### Get All Staff (should show pre-loaded staff)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff
Accept: application/json

### Create a New Task
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Process Customer Order #123",
  "description": "Handle customer order and coordinate delivery",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "assignedStaffId": "staff-1",
  "startDate": "2025-08-02",
  "dueDate": "2025-08-05",
  "createdBy": "manager-1",
  "customerReference": "CUST-123"
}

### Get Task Details (replace {taskId} with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/{taskId}
Accept: application/json

### Test Bug Fix 1: Reassign Task by Customer Reference
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/assign-by-ref?customerReference=CUST-123&newStaffId=staff-2&updatedBy=manager-1
Accept: application/json

### Test Bug Fix 2: Get Tasks by Date Range (excludes cancelled)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/date-range?startDate=2025-08-01&endDate=2025-08-10
Accept: application/json

### Test Feature 1: Smart Daily View
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/smart-daily?startDate=2025-08-02&endDate=2025-08-02
Accept: application/json

### Test Feature 2: Update Task Priority
